headline.main: An Investor Plunges Into Unknown Territory

results.snippet: Wilshire Associates manages money for clients from all over the world. But not from Kazakhstan.    ''We know very little about Kazakhstan, actually,'' said Thomas Stevens, who runs the asset management division of Wilshire, the Santa Monica, Calif.,...
results.lead_paragraph: Wilshire Associates manages money for clients from all over the world. But not from Kazakhstan. ''We know very little about Kazakhstan, actually,'' said Thomas Stevens, who runs the asset management division of Wilshire, the Santa Monica, Calif., investment firm best known for its Wilshire 5000 stock index.
